                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250630-131-off663 t18250630-131-cd664"></join>, a handkerchief, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250630-131-victim681" type="victimName">
                        Edward 
